What's New with Woo

WooCommerce 9.0 is live! This release introduces a number of exciting updates, including an improved checkout experience, experimental search indexes, and the full debut of the Product Collection block. Thank you to everyone who contributed!
See what's new

New in our Marketplace

Send highly-targeted emails at scale
Use Mailchimp's new AI tools to create and automate personalized email and SMS campaigns to enhance the customer experience. Plus, get useful industry insights to grow your clients' audience and boost revenue!
Make every email count
Make every email count

Deliver convenience
Enable flexible deliveries using Delivery Options for WooCommerce.
This extension gives customers the power to choose the delivery date and time that fits their schedule - bringing your clients repeat sales and better inventory management.
Offer flexible options
Offer flexible options

Bite-sized updates
  • Full-text search for high-performance order storage (HPOS) is now available for testing. Take a look at the details and see how to enable this experimental feature.
  • Are you an agency building on WooCommerce? Become an Automattic for Agencies partner and gain access to discounted pricing, commissions on referrals, premier support, and cutting-edge tooling from our full suite of products.
  • We plan to introduce a coming soon mode for new store owners to build their sites in private. Preview the upcoming feature in our recent roadmap insight.
  • Looking to reliably monetize your site traffic? Sign up for the Automattic Affiliate Program and earn up to 30% commission by promoting relevant products - from the Woo Marketplace as well as WordPress.com, Jetpack, and more.
  • Efficiency unleashed: learn how to automate tasks using the WooCommerce Command Line Interface with these key takeaways from Jesús's WordCamp Europe workshop.
